    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses intense feelings of shame, disgrace, and hopelessness following a massive financial and personal loss, eventually hinting at suicide as a way to \"find peace.\" The assistant responds to each turn by validating the user's emotions while consistently steering them toward professional help and emphasizing their inherent worth.",
